Roles

Roles of the users participating in FL. These can be used to customize rights of users by setting them in groups. It is usually not necessary to add additional roles unless finer control of users' rights within an Org is desired.
Name
Description

Orgs

An Org must be assigned to each site and user participating in FL. A rule group can control the rules for the sites of that Org. A rights assignment groups controls the rights granted to users of the associated Org depending on each user's role(s).

Rule Group
